-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ScoreKeeper
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ScoreKeeper eliminates the need for grabbing paper and pencil every time you 
and your friends sit down to play a card game, board game, dice game, or domino 
game. The simple interface is designed to not interfere with the main 
functionality of keeping track of players scores and letting you know who's in 
the lead. 

Site: http://caspian311.github.com/ScoreKeeper-Android


